{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.160", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Verkehrsminister! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD will eine rationale, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.880", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seri\u00f6se Verkehrspolitik gestalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.200", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.080", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was gerade in unserem Land passiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist genau das Gegenteil davon."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie vermitteln den B\u00fcrgern das Gef\u00fchl, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.920", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir lebten in einer dreckigen Umgebung mit lebensgef\u00e4hrlichem Feinstaub und Stickoxiden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fast neuwertige Dieselfahrzeuge haben drastische Wertverluste erlitten und sind von Fahrverboten bedroht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.680", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer ist daf\u00fcr eigentlich verantwortlich?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.400", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Europ\u00e4ische Union hat vor circa 20\u00a0Jahren Grenzwerte f\u00fcr Schadstoffe definiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.680", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Grenzwerte wurden begr\u00fcndet mit Studien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die aus den 90er-Jahren stammen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Verh\u00e4ltnis zu den damals gemessenen Werten in Mailand oder Rom von weit \u00fcber 130\u00a0Mikrogramm Stickoxid ist Stuttgart im Jahr\u00a02017 ein Luftkurort."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.960", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "20\u00a0Jahre hatten Sie Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.920", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Studien und die Grenzwerte zu hinterfragen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.920", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie h\u00e4tten auch die Abgasnormen der Fahrzeuge auf US-Niveau \u00e4ndern k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nichts haben Sie getan. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.480", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen setzen Sie Hunderte Millionen Euro Steuergeld f\u00fcr ein Sofortprogramm ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.600", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das man als hei\u00dfe Luft bezeichnen kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.720", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Taxen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.800", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pflegedienste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Paketdienste und Busse sollen elektrifiziert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kennen Sie eigentlich die Studien des Landesumweltamts Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.800", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche die Wirksamkeit dieser Ma\u00dfnahmen bewerten? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.680", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Studien bescheinigen den Ma\u00dfnahmen einen vernachl\u00e4ssigbaren Effekt auf Luftschadstoffe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.960", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fahrverbote und Ihre Placebo-Ma\u00dfnahmen werden die Luftqualit\u00e4t nur marginal verbessern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber einen gigantischen Schaden f\u00fcr unsere Volkswirtschaft anrichten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine weitere aktuelle EU-Gesetzesvorlage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.240", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der alle Fraktionen in diesem Haus\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "au\u00dfer unserer\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.880", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zugestimmt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.760", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird unser Leben in den n\u00e4chsten Jahren einschneidend ver\u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.600", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In dieser aktuellen Vorlage der EU wird ab 2021 die Einhaltung des durchschnittlichen Verbrauchs f\u00fcr Pkw von 4,1\u00a0Liter Benzin pro 100\u00a0Kilometer gefordert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.440", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie glauben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.360", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es m\u00f6glich ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.640", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit einer Mittelklasselimousine in einem realit\u00e4tsnahen Verbrauchstest 4,1\u00a0Liter pro 100\u00a0Kilometer zu erreichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.160", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollten Sie wieder einmal Ihr eigenes Auto nehmen und nicht den Fahrdienst."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.240", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr eine typische Mittelklasselimousine sind dann 4\u00a0000\u00a0Euro Strafzahlung f\u00e4llig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.000", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Offensichtlich glauben einige hier, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.400", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man m\u00fcsse nur die Gesetze \u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und schon sinke der Verbrauch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.920", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gesetze der Thermodynamik kann man mit demokratischen Mehrheiten nicht \u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weil wir diese utopischen Ziele mit Verbrennungsmotoren nicht erreichen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.240", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden jetzt Elektroautos gehypt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Glauben Sie ernsthaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.520", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Elektroautos verursachen weniger CO 2 ? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.960", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Woher kommt denn der Strom f\u00fcr die Elektroautos? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.200", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kenne keine Ausbaupl\u00e4ne der Stromerzeugung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.480", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die absehbar dazu f\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.320", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir einen CO 2 -freien Strommix in Deutschland haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau wie bei den utopisch niedrigen Stickoxidgrenzwerten haben Sie auch bei der CO 2 -Vorgabe die technische Machbarkeit nicht ber\u00fccksichtigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt vern\u00fcnftige Rahmenbedingungen zu setzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.280", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stolpern Sie von der Diskussion \u00fcber Fahrverbote f\u00fcr Dieselfahrzeuge in das CO 2 -Grenzwerte-Desaster."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.960", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Verkehrspolitik eines modernen Industriestaates geh\u00f6rt es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.600", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wirtschaftliche sowie freiheitlich-individuelle Interessen als auch Umweltschutzbelange austariert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.480", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr steht die AfD."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.120", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Offenbar sind wir hier die Einzigen in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.000", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat die Kollegin Kirsten L\u00fchmann von der SPD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}